  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nValidator 258098 missed its duties at epoch 93025, slot 2976826\r\n<img width=\"939\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-05-11 at 13 22 02\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/167782191-37c6ef7b-1250-4921-93c9-2b75263bcb3f.png\">\r\n\r\nIn the validator log\r\n```\r\nMay-11 02:34:48.819[]                ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: Signed attestation slot=2976774, index=23, head=0xb4e289c97354dfb8c2384b1b2bb1a52d2ba68aa92ebe8b8281646e94bbb6d361, validatorIndex=258098\r\n...\r\nMay-11 02:48:04.081[]                ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: Signed attestation slot=2976840, index=18, head=0x679df2b452091f1f14037a1aa5f7cef369d6866086b61cd34df5a403f897c18e, validatorIndex=258098\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nValidator should not miss any attestation duties",
